      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "直接用时间片序号吧，从0开始。这样更贴合Round Robin的调度逻辑。axisFormat就用%s显示秒数或者序号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "datef",
        "axisf"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，dateFormat设为X，axisFormat设为%s。那标题我拟定为\"Planificación Round Robin (Retail_CouponSystem) - Parte 1 (Retail_PointOfSale)\"，您看可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "retail couponsystem",
        "retail pointofsale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，标题要突出这是优惠券系统的调度规划，同时注明Parte 1和PointOfSale的关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我打算分两个secti：CPU和I/O。CPU部分放P1到P4的执行区间，I/O部分放对应的IO操作。这样结构清晰吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "secti",
        "p1",
        "p2",
        "p3",
        "p4",
        "p1 io",
        "p2 io",
        "p4 io"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "结构没问题。不过要注意，P1、P2、P3、P4在CPU部分会多次出现，因为Round Robin会轮转调度。另外P4_IO要特别关注，它涉及CustomerLoyalty。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1",
        "p2",
        "p3",
        "p4",
        "p4 io",
        "retail customerloyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
